===Stage 4===
;3 May 2014&nbsp;— [[Fribourg]] to Fribourg, {{convert|173.1|km|1|abbr=on}}<ref>{{cite web|title=Stage 4: Fribourg to Fribourg|url=http://www.cyclingnews.com/races/tour-de-romandie-2014-2014/stage-4|work=[[cyclingnews.com]]|publisher=[[Future plc]]|accessdate=29 April 2014}}</ref>

